@joel done updating the Forms of MS to all clinical trials posts however the issue persists. Could you please check? Thanks!

Hi Rica,

Thank you for getting back to me. The "forms of MS" filter only works when two check boxes are ticked. For example, "relapsing forms of MS" and "secondary progressive MS" both need to be selected to see either of those. If I just select one, nothing comes up, even if a particular trial is only suited to people with one of those forms of MS. Could you please fix this?

Thank you for all your help.

Best wishes,
